headline: Weyerhaeuser Q4 Earnings Call Highlights
summary: Weyerhaeuser (NYSE:WY) management emphasized portfolio optimization, expanding “climate solutions” offerings, and disciplined capital allocation as the company closed out 2025 amid what executives repeatedly described as extremely challenging lumber and OSB markets. On the call, CEO Devin Stockfish
